data.description: *Buyer Perk!!* Sellers are offering a $10,000 credit that can be applied towards the buyer's closing costs or used for a rate buy-down. Nestled in Colonial Valley, this 2,240 sqft, 3-bed, 2-bath home stands as a testament to one family's cherished memories. The spacious kitchen is perfect for gatherings, and the main-floor master suite offers convenience. From the newer deck, take in the serene mountain views--a hint of its prime location. With a modern roof overhead and only minutes from downtown Grants Pass, this property marries its rich history with the promise of new stories to come. Don't miss out; schedule your viewing today!''
